{
  "stem": "19210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was involved with the convoys between Nahariya and, and Haifa and Kiryat Bialik and Kiryat Motzkin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but these convoys did not consist of bringing arms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were convoys that simply because there had been instances where the Arabs had, if, if you caught a single car or truck or motorcycle, people were killed, all right?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this case, we used to get-- gather the, the buses and the trucks and delivery trucks and whatever it is and wait until the majority of these trucks get together.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in those cars then there would be a Haganah escort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in most, in most cases armed with a-- the lieutenant would be armed only.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many of the girls, the women, play a great role in that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they used to hide also arms with them-- hand grenades or small, small firearms.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on the, on the way to Haifa, on the way to Nahariya, we used to bring supplies-- obviously, food supplies and whatever supplies needed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people that worked in, in Haifa used to travel by convoys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I traveled many, many times by convoys, many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was late in one convoy and two convoys, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in here, I did help some of the Hungarian refugees that had been unloaded some time earlier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was leaving Kiryat Motzkin towards Haifa, towards Nahariya, also at the time that my wife was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and I lost the convoy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I arrived too late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided to, to do it on my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I carried with me an Arabic kaffiyeh, a headgear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because I was so dark as it is, and I could pass very easily for, for an Arab, at least at the time-- very dark, black hair, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
